                                    </div>

                                    <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                        <span class="text-fuchsia-400">📸</span>
                                        <div>
                                            <div class="text-white font-medium">
                                                Screenshot to Code
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="text-gray-400">
                                                Transforma screenshots en
                                                editable components
