                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                                Computer Vision Magic
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm">
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Sketch Recognition:</strong> AI identifica
                                    shapes, text y layouts
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Screenshot Analysis:</strong> Extrae
                                    components y structure
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Image Understanding:</strong> Recognizes
