                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div
                            class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-pink-500/20"
                        >
                            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🔗</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                                Smart Component System
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm">
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Component Recognition:</strong> Identifica
                                    reusable elements
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Pattern Library:</strong> Auto-builds
                                    design systems
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Variant Generation:</strong> Creates
                                    component states
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Consistency Enforcement:</strong> Maintains
                                    design standards
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div
                            class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-violet-600/20"
                        >
                            <div class="text-3xl mb-4">⚡</div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                                Code Generation
